title: Waitangi: What Really Happened
actors: George Henare, Rawiri Paratene, Calvin Tuteao, Jarod Rawiri
plot: A dramatization of the days leading up to 6 February 1840 when the gathered Maori leaders signed the Treaty of Waitangi, told in recreations and interviews with the participants and locals.
name: Waitangi: What Really Happened
